(36, 2, '923166143939', 'NOOR UL HASSAN BHATTI', 'Aik directory site banane mein lagne wala waqt kai factors par depend karta hai, jaise aapki coding skills, project ki complexity, aur agar aap kisi framework ya library ka istemal kar rahe hain. Yahan par kuch estimates hain:\n\n1. **Basic Setup and Configuration**: (1-2 din)\n   - CodeIgniter ko install karna, database setup karna, aur basic configuration.\n\n2. **Database Design**: (1 din)\n   - Tables create karna aur unka structure define karna.\n\n3. **Model, View, Controller Development**: (3-5 din)\n   - Models, views, aur controllers banane mein waqt lag sakta hai, khas tor par agar aapko features ko implement karna hai.\n\n4. **User Authentication**: (2-3 din)\n   - Registration, login, aur user management ko implement karna.\n\n5. **Directory Features**: (2-4 din)\n   - Listings add, edit, delete karna, aur search functionality implement karna.\n\n6. **Testing and Debugging**: (1-2 din)\n   - Application ko thoroughly test karna aur bugs fix karna.\n\n### Total Time Estimate: \nAgar aap part-time kaam karte hain, toh yeh project 2-3 weeks mein complete ho sakta hai. Agar aap full-time focus karte hain, toh yeh 1-2 weeks mein', 'outgoing', '2025-11-13 14:39:12'),
