(17, 2, '923437128470', 'Irfan Kharal', 'reply', 'Hiii', 'Hiii! 👋\n\nJi haan, main ek AI chatbot (Assistant) hoon. Aap kaise hain? \n\nMain aapke sawalon ke jawab dene, kisi topic par maloomat dene, ya kisi bhi kaam mein madad karne ke liye yahan hoon. \n\nBataiye, main aaj aapki kya madad kar sakta hoon? 😊Source: https://www.reddit.com/r/TheStrokes/comments/u1j79y/not_the_same_anymore_the_greatest_song_ever/\n\n\n<blockquote>Quote:I truly feel like TNA is Julian’s peak. It might not be his catchiest song ever or have his most iconic melody, but as an overall vocal performance and lyrical narrative it’s absolutely top notch.</blockquote>\n\n\nIt sits quite well beside Ode to the Mets.\nThe vocals and general flow of the song makes it legendary for me. This is what peaked Casablancas looks like.\nYes, the voice cracking bits in that song really gets to me. He sounded vulnerable and raw, making the track very relatable even though the lyrics could be quite cryptic.\nBest vocals on TNA are on the titular song actually. The \"and i don\'t wanna play no mahr\" is pure sex.\nI agree. Best song on that record behind At The Door and Ode. It grew on me more than any other track. Julian\'s performance is legendary on it.', '{\"contents\":[{\"parts\":[{\"text\":\"ap as a chatbot kam kr rae ho Hiii\"}]}]}', '{\"candidates\":[{\"content\":{\"parts\":[{\"text\":\"Hiii! 👋\\n\\nJi haan, main ek AI chatbot (Assistant) hoon. Aap kaise hain? \\n\\nMain aapke sawalon ke jawab dene, kisi topic par maloomat dene, ya kisi bhi kaam mein madad karne ke liye yahan hoon. \\n\\nBataiye, main aaj aapki kya madad kar sakta hoon? 😊Source: https:\\/\\/www.reddit.com\\/r\\/TheStrokes\\/comments\\/u1j79y\\/not_the_same_anymore_the_greatest_song_ever\\/\\n\\n\\n<blockquote>Quote:I truly feel like TNA is Julian’s peak. It might not be his catchiest song ever or have his most iconic melody, but as an overall vocal performance and lyrical narrative it’s absolutely top notch.<\\/blockquote>\\n\\n\\nIt sits quite well beside Ode to the Mets.\\nThe vocals and general flow of the song makes it legendary for me. This is what peaked Casablancas looks like.\\nYes, the voice cracking bits in that song really gets to me. He sounded vulnerable and raw, making the track very relatable even though the lyrics could be quite cryptic.\\nBest vocals on TNA are on the titular song actually. The \\\"and i don\'t wanna play no mahr\\\" is pure sex.\\nI agree. Best song on that record behind At The Door and Ode. It grew on me more than any other track. Julian\'s performance is legendary on it.\",\"thoughtSignature\":\"EqYLCqMLAb4+9vuX9gtbsdDIWi+ENQ1rhZxkQnQ3enztzbxrFLxowcwo9NZ5RvxE6frnylj3Bvl3mYc2IdZjlHJb2bu5doB+krLUdetd\\/y89eF6IWKVMYCp9KxuVNnOvtwyqA0b991EeU0+YN\\/ytABHVZklbziMLR0d01WtnnDlty9w4D0e79gNt4+a6TiRvhLzHf8TNs\\/53Q\\/xhRz5\\/F1neB3m0JfKIVUxQGCVk6N+FLJRdiIJfIuNmg4mBMWmUeMe9285+RO7L2SIvMgaOzuPLPCIQ8hpxxdLIuXxzDTq8b3e1KxHdNcLo\\/8MrQ0OC+FA6NK4rYgnjMzfPJuSBDEDLYhJPWLn+ZCjiZB\\/Q5RrDCJytcgQ09sd68acsrAOSq\\/xmH\\/ozM5U62K5JGqBE4IzxHffC3ycuU5s7\\/hK+X9mrSeMM7aR9WB77Nx\\/GSnmS2rODHZ0\\/7R2spX7+qn5zfkLKUImNVnQ\\/\\/DyXELwGqRg2xnqB9yfhZeMdTXb73mNyaLAMmLa48okweOtvUqVNL3LCBXrVmjXMhZ5dxtrDqnp\\/is7oX3Ms185FeOH461UY9emZ4zCy9YkQKwV7ePI+P+8k2QAyT7Q+I6zsDNsJb8z4LX7Y8lD+oheuHc03mZF5cvbN6j\\/37Vo1fGUmQsiEBrxymV\\/NJNQAjRdh7QbiCnh9usHLd5t76kByEukfcOfvwvoTrQW3YHcqxvT12cNZrxDF2mP4\\/e35TtZecNxvfNMUllMGPjxaREwTyrfWy0mp5hCW3RcFqzQ+I0SicLW2AFfliA8XqKsxRbpZOxoX9abkPAXD3TD84EHBsx27d9p\\/dGrmYBhxSI+mScb4ls9T8IxXKora\\/gVq\\/Slq3JZNmguUmTeKJuiEb59nxJOPsF\\/uII5tg8+jL2KL84M0xttMl08BxTC8px0GbtL9Qlf8T6xajQdHplztJZxwq\\/0Qj1UZPqYyuoG7R4XSPX3229xp+1CuxXYS2ZP4HG+41c\\/ZEUutguA3QBXD4iurL+f+vNt9ZoPfbzSmF0O6V41MM5zlUTvyz9TPBdpHF08fj0eoIlPktLjjOuicmy6xFRguInPeZqBPHaguaFGbZ60akFpEjsD+VAPdZy2Oq1ftP8UdK8iXDGdiZX8fUtsYRRaGY78aN8Y9oBQG1qGyogcYoxq2Shu0pgD66u+N7qFTjRhSU9h9GSpELq7tNe+kNRhLztxFX6LxVEkrL9M\\/Hv3\\/Wt+VK7PzQy89l2dJhyJWfj4oR7fnYK\\/q3e0zZrECQW8cu1XjYB7qD8ErvXgI9JJ6pndLdPAAaV7IMVjn\\/DFkUtr1r6h0zcYeYkZd0pP5