(35, 2, '923166143939', '', 'Aapko CodeIgniter mein aik directory site banane ke liye kuch steps aur features ki zarurat hogi. Yahan aik basic outline hai jo aapko shuru karne mein madad karegi:\n\n### Basic Features:\n1. **User Registration/Login**: Users ko register aur login karne ki facility.\n2. **Directory Listings**: Users ko listings add, edit, aur delete karne ki facility.\n3. **Search Functionality**: Listings ko search karne ka option.\n4. **Categories**: Different categories mein listings ko organize karna.\n5. **Admin Panel**: Admin ke liye ek panel jahan wo listings ko manage kar sakein.\n\n### Development Steps:\n1. **Setup CodeIgniter**:\n   - CodeIgniter ko download karein aur apne server par install karein.\n\n2. **Database Creation**:\n   - Aik database banayein aur tables create karein (e.g., users, listings, categories).\n\n3. **Models, Views, and Controllers (MVC)**:\n   - CodeIgniter ka MVC structure istemal karte hue models, views, aur controllers banayein.\n\n4. **User Authentication**:\n   - User registration aur login functionality implement karein.\n\n5. **Directory Management**:\n   - Listings add, edit, aur delete karne ke liye functionality banayein.\n\n6. **Search and Filter**:\n   - Listings ko search aur filter karne', '{\"to\":\"+923166143939\",\"text\":\"Aapko CodeIgniter mein aik directory site banane ke liye kuch steps aur features ki zarurat hogi. Yahan aik basic outline hai jo aapko shuru karne mein madad karegi:\\n\\n### Basic Features:\\n1. **User Registration\\/Login**: Users ko register aur login karne ki facility.\\n2. **Directory Listings**: Users ko listings add, edit, aur delete karne ki facility.\\n3. **Search Functionality**: Listings ko search karne ka option.\\n4. **Categories**: Different categories mein listings ko organize karna.\\n5. **Admin Panel**: Admin ke liye ek panel jahan wo listings ko manage kar sakein.\\n\\n### Development Steps:\\n1. **Setup CodeIgniter**:\\n   - CodeIgniter ko download karein aur apne server par install karein.\\n\\n2. **Database Creation**:\\n   - Aik database banayein aur tables create karein (e.g., users, listings, categories).\\n\\n3. **Models, Views, and Controllers (MVC)**:\\n   - CodeIgniter ka MVC structure istemal karte hue models, views, aur controllers banayein.\\n\\n4. **User Authentication**:\\n   - User registration aur login functionality implement karein.\\n\\n5. **Directory Management**:\\n   - Listings add, edit, aur delete karne ke liye functionality banayein.\\n\\n6. **Search and Filter**:\\n   - Listings ko search aur filter karne\"}', '{\"success\":true,\"data\":{\"msgId\":11114645,\"jid\":\"+923166143939\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}', 200, 1, '', '2025-11-13 14:30:06'),
(36, 2, '923166143939', 'NOOR UL HASSAN BHATTI', 'Aapko CodeIgniter mein ek directory site banane ke liye kuch basic steps aur code snippets ki zaroorat hogi. Yahan par main aapko ek simple structure aur kuch guidance de raha hoon.\n\n### Steps to Create a Directory Site in CodeIgniter\n\n1. **Install CodeIgniter**: Pehle CodeIgniter ko apne server ya local machine par install karein.\n\n2. **Create Database**: Apne database mein ek table create karein jahan aap directory entries store karenge. \n\n   ```sql\n   CREATE TABLE directory (\n       id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,\n       name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,\n       description TEXT,\n       created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n   );\n   ```\n\n3. **Create Model**: Ek model banayein jo database se data fetch karega.\n\n   ```php\n   // application/models/Directory_model.php\n   class Directory_model extends CI_Model {\n       public function __construct() {\n           $this->load->database();\n       }\n\n       public function get_entries() {\n           $query = $this->db->get(\'directory\');\n           return $query->result_array();\n       }\n\n       public function add_entry($data) {\n           return $this->db->insert(\'directory\', $data);\n       }\n   }\n   ```\n\n4. **Create Controller**: Ek controller banayein jo model se data interact karega.\n\n   ```php\n   // application', '{\"to\":\"+923166143939\",\"text\":\"Aapko CodeIgniter mein ek directory site banane ke liye kuch basic steps aur code snippets ki zaroorat hogi. Yahan par main aapko ek simple structure aur kuch guidance de raha hoon.\\n\\n### Steps to Create a Directory Site in CodeIgniter\\n\\n1. **Install CodeIgniter**: Pehle CodeIgniter ko apne server ya local machine par install karein.\\n\\n2. **Create Database**: Apne database mein ek table create karein jahan aap directory entries store karenge. \\n\\n   ```sql\\n   CREATE TABLE directory (\\n       id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,\\n       name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,\\n       description TEXT,\\n       created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\\n   );\\n   ```\\n\\n3. **Create Model**: Ek model banayein jo database se data fetch karega.\\n\\n   ```php\\n   \\/\\/ application\\/models\\/Directory_model.php\\n   class Directory_model extends CI_Model {\\n       public function __construct() {\\n           $this->load->database();\\n       }\\n\\n       public function get_entries() {\\n           $query = $this->db->get(\'directory\');\\n           return $query->result_array();\\n       }\\n\\n       public function add_entry($data) {\\n           return $this->db->insert(\'directory\', $data);\\n       }\\n   }\\n   ```\\n\\n4. **Create Controller**: Ek controller banayein jo model se data interact karega.\\n\\n   ```php\\n   \\/\\/ application\"}', '{\"message\":\"You are on a free trial. You can send 1 message every 1 minute.\",\"retry_after\":60,\"help\":\"Upgrade to a paid plan to increase your rate limit.\"}', 429, 0, '', '2025-11-13 14:30:06'),
